{
  "text": "Given this very general setup, Ref. [CITATION_1] asked the following question: What is the minimum value \u221a s min of the parton-level Mandelstam invariant mass variable \u221a s which is consistent with the observed visible 4-momentum vector P \u00b5 \u2261 (E, P )? As it turned out, the answer to this question is given by the universal formula [CITATION_2] ",
